summary: Taylor swift came on stage. This was the moment I had waited for for years. Right when this clip ends is where I screamed that’s...
caption: Taylor swift came on stage. This was the moment I had waited for for years. Right when this clip ends is where I screamed that’s my baby and basically fell to the floor shaking and laugh cried and looked insane because I couldn’t even process her actually being there. Then I just suddenly got back up and screamed all the words to RFI, crazy meme danced with my glow stick and it was like I didn’t even have anxiety or any kind of self preservation when everyone turned and starred at me. I lived my best meme life.

summary:
Dear @taylorswift, 
I’m not sure I have words to express how much last night’s show meant to me, but I am going to try. 
The...
body:
Dear @taylorswift,

I’m not sure I have words to express how much last night’s show meant to me, but I am going to try.

The last time I saw you in concert was in 2013 on the Red tour and I wasn’t sure if I would ever have a better concert experience than that, however here I am…

You constantly make an effort to show fans how much you truly care for them, which is rare in the entertainment industry these days, you go above and beyond to make sure those in the very back row have just as great of an experience as those in the very front row. You listen to fans, we wanted to hear So It Goes… and you performed it (for the first time ever, too!).

I’m so incredibly thankful for you and your music and have been since I first heard Love Story and began exploring your discography.

So, thank you, Taylor. I will always hold you dear in my heart and will never forget last night as long as I live.

I love you.

From,

Ellie x


@taylornation
